Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙 不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.79,0:02:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.69,0:02:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.45,0:02:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.98,0:02:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和昨天一样 感觉杀机而避开攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.35,0:02:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个真合身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.49,0:02:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.46,0:02:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不必那么用力的打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.44,0:03:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用点力打就没有意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.87,0:03:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想被打的话你快点儿能避开不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.93,0:03:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前又没有睁着眼睛训练过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就这样怎么可能做到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.93,0:03:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为能感觉到杀机 简单的攻击应该可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.29,0:03:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手会出什么招就跟猜拳一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.77,0:03:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.08,0:03:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么猜拳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久之前才学会的 还说得一副了不起的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还装得像很懂一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.26,0:03:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 吵死了 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,训练中不许说不相关的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 干嘛突然攻击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击就是突如其来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.85,0:03:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.13,0:03:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不像样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为你说了些不相关的事情才会这么狼狈的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说让你等等的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.65,0:03:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等等就不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:03:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人是不会等你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可这是训练啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.19,0:04:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找借口可是丢脸的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.40,0:04:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 破了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.47,0:04:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是“徒”的话 你就被吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 今天就到这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得准备去上学了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.47,0:04:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.73,0:04:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 小悠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是悠二他擅自结束的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.73,0:04:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为训练不能顺利进行下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然好像被打惨的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.61,0:04:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的明明更加不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可那时都一副没事的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.43,0:04:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能他觉察到自己丢脸的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.10,0:04:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.61,0:04:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为小夏娜是这么可爱又小的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你打了对男孩子来说是有些丢脸的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我比较厉害 也是没有办法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.21,0:05:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是呢 男孩子爱面子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是在希望自己被女孩子在意的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.49,0:05:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在意悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对悠二来说只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.43,0:05:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天放学后张开“封绝” 我们训练能大幅移动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就做大规模的训练没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是为了没问题才要训练的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.33,0:05:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对男孩子来说是很丢脸的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,训练的话 之中一定会有丢脸的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.38,0:05:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算是在鼓励我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.68,0:06:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是说理所当然的事情罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.35,0:06:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就觉得相当丢脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.06,0:06:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢脸这种事 没什么好在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是悠二你变强后一起战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.77,0:06:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.20,0:06:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有一元的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去小卖部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.75,0:06:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 大姐头的情况怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:07:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是大姐头她恢复了就会离开这个城市吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.95,0:07:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并没有想让大姐头恢复原状…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.73,0:07:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好饿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪方同学 我们一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.05,0:07:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.06,0:07:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这些都是一美你作的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是吉田同学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.23,0:07:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为朋友给了我菜谱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.52,0:07:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.44,0:07:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 请吃吧 不喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.24,0:07:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由香里你愿意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.31,0:07:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个和卖的完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.85,0:07:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.15,0:07:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同学 你很擅长作料理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:08:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只是比较喜欢而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.81,0:08:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是好吃 但也不好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰一下 有图书员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有 我和她就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.65,0:08:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.15,0:08:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说图书室的书本摆放位置要突然变更
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.45,0:08:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学后到图书室集合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今…今天？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各班都要两名 不行的话找个人代替你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.02,0:08:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去看望奶奶呢 我们一家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么坂井 你就替她跟吉田同学去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.86,0:08:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也得去补习班
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.24,0:08:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该有空的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.39,0:08:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同学 这样行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是会不会添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定了是两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:08:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you！帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.58,0:09:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.63,0:09:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.90,0:09:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.56,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.58,0:09:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天放学后张开“封绝” 我们训练能大幅移动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.48,0:09:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你们有什么约好的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 说今天让平井同学把笔记给我看的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.32,0:09:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学 下次好吗 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.25,0:09:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是我拜托的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.67,0:09:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.16,0:09:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是因为是学生会的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,训练的话 晚上也可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.07,0:09:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说好了今天放学后训练的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.04,0:10:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是没有办法的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.59,0:10:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒绝不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经都答应人家了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.48,0:10:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经拒绝不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.90,0:10:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,训练不是更重要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.24,0:10:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个嘛……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.61,0:10:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 学校…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.95,0:10:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些都无关紧要的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.70,0:10:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是我这边先约好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.66,0:10:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我是来道歉的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.46,0:10:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说想要训练的不是悠二你自己吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不训练又不会死人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二你不够认真
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.74,0:10:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.34,0:10:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之今天不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.01,0:10:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.41,0:10:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有你那样任性的说的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.04,0:10:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会出席学生会的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二你不训练的话是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相当弱而且还相当丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就你现在那样就完全帮不上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.87,0:10:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.26,0:10:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.66,0:10:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有生气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.97,0:11:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是就只是说说而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.41,0:11:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.72,0:11:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同学 吉田和坂井加班吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.83,0:11:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 小夏娜你一个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小悠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.78,0:11:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天好像学生会有事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.14,0:11:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么到屋里来等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.98,0:11:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作了好吃的布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.19,0:11:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夏娜一个人生活 真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.59,0:11:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经都习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.30,0:11:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃 千草做的真是太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夏娜 一起吃晚饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.37,0:12:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.59,0:12:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 回去的时候就跟坂井同学两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.41,0:12:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是中途没话可说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.05,0:12:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.42,0:12:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 刚才我听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.61,0:12:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2班的平井同学在测验中全是100分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.60,0:12:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 听说在体育上也是表现非凡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是少有的天才呢 那个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.88,0:12:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.94,0:12:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.53,0:12:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:13:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想问 关于由香里的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直这样一个人想的话 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎样看待由香里的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.91,0:13:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才3班的人在说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厉害的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.89,0:13:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯 真的是很厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.00,0:13:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.24,0:13:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜她太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.04,0:13:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 笨蛋 真是多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.89,0:13:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.73,0:13:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小悠你好晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夏娜都已经吃完晚饭洗了澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是我以前的 小夏娜说要穿穿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.23,0:13:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯 不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.08,0:13:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都很晚了 你快送送她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.78,0:13:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是知道晚上夏娜住在我房间里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.05,0:13:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈她会生气的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.96,0:14:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天本来要做的训练
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.43,0:14:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 今天已经很晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.90,0:14:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底还只是个凡人而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.73,0:14:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让“徒”吃了也没关系 “Flamehaze”也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.99,0:14:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,习惯战斗的话 悠二…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:14:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.03,0:15:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“存在之力”我的“存在之力”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是什么啊 是“磷子”吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太菜鸟级的“封绝”啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.05,0:15:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.70,0:15:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.85,0:15:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？“悼词的咏手”怎么会这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.71,0:15:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是都这样了 有什么办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.64,0:15:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一句话就能搞定的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.78,0:15:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好 交给小鬼头就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.33,0:15:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二不会来 悠二不会来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.52,0:15:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊 对我 悠二只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.25,0:16:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个在干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.06,0:16:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经暴走了 恐怕是失去了主人的“磷子”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了主人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么不管它的话多少时间会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.41,0:16:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算“磷子”吞食多少“存在之力”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.70,0:16:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能成为自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.03,0:16:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“Flamehaze”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀害了主人的杀戮的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是杀不了我的 我是不会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.87,0:16:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.97,0:16:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着吧 我会吞食“存在之力”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.97,0:16:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我的…我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.90,0:17:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 这家伙的身体 软乎乎的好难砍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.85,0:17:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的“存在之力”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要砍 不要消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.36,0:17:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要出门去什么地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.99,0:17:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才起就心神不宁地静不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.51,0:17:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直看着外面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.91,0:17:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是跟朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也没什么关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.56,0:17:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.06,0:17:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为去了也帮不上什么忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.14,0:17:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是这样说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.19,0:17:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是你这样说的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.82,0:17:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“存在…存在之力”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.51,0:17:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞食地再多你也会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会消失的 不会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:18:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算身型巨大 本体的核心也是看起来很小的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.39,0:18:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在把它破坏之前只能这样持续地砍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又把我的“存在之力”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.83,0:18:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然 把我的“存在之力”……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说过不行了的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 好痛……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.80,0:18:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的……存在 不要消失啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 吵死了 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.24,0:18:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.62,0:18:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.56,0:18:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那个朋友 不是希望你能帮上她的忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.29,0:18:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为只要在她身边就能成为她的力量的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.37,0:18:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢待了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.03,0:19:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为只要在她身边就能成为她的力量的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 夏娜她就算没有我也能战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.24,0:19:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为夏娜她很强的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜 夏娜……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.04,0:19:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是“磷子”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.53,0:19:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我不要消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.38,0:19:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.86,0:20:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的“存在之…”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.34,0:20:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜 夏娜你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 又没有受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.13,0:20:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情已经都习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.35,0:20:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有点累而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.02,0:20:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.21,0:20:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好痛苦啊 悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人 好痛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.94,0:20:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.49,0:20:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.25,0:20:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢下你一个人 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.79,0:20:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二 变强吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:20:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加的强大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.65,0:20:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我会的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.85,0:20:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会变强的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.17,0:21:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了能一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.30,0:21:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好脏啊 又不是扔垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.85,0:21:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 太厉害了 这家伙真是太有钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个集团的少爷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.22,0:21:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 没劲儿的说些什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来的是四号击手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.38,0:21:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我住手 你们这些垃圾鼠辈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.17,0:21:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不错 这家伙是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.28,0:21:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 同情他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.79,0:21:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长大人 不行的吧 让你等着我你就不等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.22,0:21:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好好等着的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.02,0:21:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没有吃这些家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.71,0:21:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 兄长大人真是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.44,0:21:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.06,0:21:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的 兄长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.06,0:22:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客气尽情享用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.89,0:22:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起啊 兄长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.84,0:22:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都有好好留下“torch”的份
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.23,0:22:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为蒂丽艾尔说不那样是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.17,0:22:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴啊 兄长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.20,0:22:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 兄妹之间真做得出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.11,0:22:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱染自-索拉特和爱染他-蒂丽艾尔
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,==========================================Next EP Start==========================================
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.14,0:24:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想作为一名少女而成长的“Flamehaze”
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.61,0:24:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她所遇到并重视的阿拉斯托尔和千草
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.49,0:24:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜她所了解的相誓之恋是……
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.59,0:24:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 悠二和夏娜和Kiss
